"The bend tool can be used in any case where you might want to bend a "
"shape in two with a gradual transition between both sides."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:27
msgid ""
"This may take a little getting used to, the basics are listed below "
"controls are noted here:"
