#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:29
msgid "The initial position of the cursors define the axis to bend on."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:30
msgid ""
"The distance of the mouse-cursor to the 3D-cursor controls how sharp the "
"bend will be."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:31
msgid ""
"The relative angle of the mouse-cursor to the initial axis defines the "
"bend angle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/bend.rst:33
msgid ""
"If this seems overly complicated, its probably best to try the tool where"
" it becomes quickly apparent how the tool reacts to your input."
